        private static int staticPatientId
        static variable to keep track of the patients ids at first patientClassId is equal to 0 when the first patient arrives, its id is set to patientClassId (=0) then patientClassId is increased, so that when the next patient arrives, its id will be equal to patientClassId (=1) and so on...
